## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

```lua
-- ❌ Global variables
myGlobalVar = 10

-- ❌ Tight coupling
local playerCoins = workspace.Player.Coins.Value

-- ❌ Hard-coded values
if damage == 100 then ... end

-- ❌ Nested callbacks (callback hell)
event1:Connect(function()
    event2:Connect(function()
        event3:Connect(function()
            -- Too deep!
        end)
    end)
end)
```

